  "description": "A breathtaking sunset view featuring a bridge spanning a body of water. The sky is ablaze with vibrant oranges and reds, creating a dramatic and fiery backdrop. The bridge, silhouetted against the bright sky, is a key structural element, consisting of multiple arches and towering pylons. The water reflects the colors of the sky, creating a shimmering effect.  Dark foliage frames the scene on both sides, adding depth and a sense of natural enclosure. The overall composition feels serene and majestic.",
